description: Forest Department - Order to declare - Masimbula Forest in Masimbula D/S Division Godakawela and Demanagammana Forest in D/S Division Pelmadulla both in Ratnapura District, Gannoruwa Forest (Part) in Gannoruwa D/S Division Yatinuwara and Madeniya Hinnamuduna alias Maldeniyagala Forest in D/S Division Ududumbara and Maha Hurigolla Forest D/S Division Medadumbara all in Kandy District as conservation Forests
